<task id="task_BAE5AA642E4B4CC3894670811C7C700C">
  <title>Pin a card to a board</title>
  <shortdesc>Pin a card onto another board. If the board has not been created,
	 you can create a new board in this procedure. 
  </shortdesc>
  <prolog>
    <metadata>
      <othermeta name="solution" content="Marketing Cloud" />
    </metadata>
  </prolog>
  <taskbody>
    <steps id="steps_CA0C05855E934AFB8454D9376FF76790">
      <step id="step_58EE3203250F47B99BBEB65EEF5E83AB">
        <cmd> In the left navigation menu, click 
			 <uicontrol>Feed</uicontrol>. 
		  </cmd>
        <info>
          <p>Alternatively, click 
				<uicontrol>Boards</uicontrol>, then click the desired board to
				display its contents. 
			 </p>
        </info>
      </step>
      <step id="step_D63833863C1941DCA07E6AC70BBBBA3A">
        <cmd>Hover your cursor over the card, then click 
			 <uicontrol>Pin Card to Board</uicontrol>. 
			 <image href="graphics/pin_icon_small.png" id="image_34966523B2F042EF8FF04854F4AABC96"></image></cmd>
        <stepresult>
          <p>
            <image href="graphics/right_click_card_options.png" id="image_43E5BA7705B14F1AAEEBDAAAAFD20227">
              <?xm-replace_text Paragraph?>
            </image>
          </p>
          <p>On a tablet, long-press the desired card to display additional
				options. 
			 </p>
        </stepresult>
      </step>
      <step id="step_08A4E43580074AE9BCB91F961D188FAA">
        <cmd>Select the board(s), then click 
			 <uicontrol>View</uicontrol> to see the card in the selected board. 
		  </cmd>
        <stepresult>
          <p>
            <image href="graphics/pin_card_window1.png" id="image_3DCD3D106B3041EBA635CBCEE8738A03">
              <?xm-replace_text Paragraph?>
            </image>
          </p>
        </stepresult>
      </step>
      <step id="step_FF13CF13653B4DBB8424D1A682CC58F7">
        <cmd>Click 
			 <uicontrol>View</uicontrol> to display the board to which you pinned
			 the card. 
		  </cmd>
      </step>
    </steps>
    <result id="result_5B0B55F3EE994F78A4F8E75679AA10EE">You can also create a
		new board during this process. 
		<ol id="ol_22670E11391541A8B21939A73C9F9DE0"><li id="li_51D7AA24E39B4765A9D6B52F0359D656">Click 
			 <image href="graphics/icon_create_board.png" id="image_BD7ED6154FE34A94BAE483E64A7C4D25"></image> to create a new board on
			 which you can pin the card. 
			 <p><image href="graphics/pin_card_window2.png" id="image_1C2DABC09FB44E6AAE13C6FBF62A430D"><?xm-replace_text Step Result?></image></p></li><li id="li_37A9FDE3481E42B9A9EB0CEBC0236F5F">In the 
			 <uicontrol>Create Board</uicontrol> field, specify the name for the
			 new board, then click 
			 <uicontrol>OK</uicontrol>. 
		  </li></ol></result>
  </taskbody>
</task>